クラスの概要
Downloader Download facade class.
DownloadInfo Value object to specify download target
DownloadOption Option class to specify Downloader behavior.
DownloadOption.Builder Builder for DownloadOption

DownloadError Error types for Downloader.EXTRA_ERROR
